| Copy the specified fonts into CacheFS to allow access to this font even when network "goes away"
WimpSlot -min 256K -max 256K
CDir Cache:$.!Fonts
Access Cache:$.!Fonts LRW/r
CDir Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius
Access Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius LRW/r
CDir Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius.Book
Access Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius.Book LRW/r
FCopy <Obey$Dir>.Caius.Book.IntMetric0 Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius.Book.IntMetric0
Access Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius.Book.IntMetric0 LRW/r
FCopy <Obey$Dir>.Caius.Book.Outlines0 Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius.Book.Outlines0
Access Cache:$.!Fonts.Caius.Book.Outlines0 LRW/r
FontInstall Cache:$.!Fonts.
